Package com.complexible.common.rdf.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Namespaces
    A simple class used for management of namespaces.
    StardogBuiltInLiteral
    Interface for Stardog literals to provide datatypes as StardogValueFactory.Datatype) for more efficient processing.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractStardogCalendarLiteral
    Abstract base class for all different calendar datatypes (cf XMLGregorianCalendar.getXMLSchemaType()).
    ArrayLiteral
    Literal consisted of an array of Stardog IDs
    BuiltInLiteralUtils
    A couple of simple utility methods for dealing with builtin literals and their datatypes.
    StardogBooleanLiteral
    Custom implementation of a boolean typed literal
    StardogDurationLiteral
    Different kinds of durations.
    StardogLongIntegerLiteral
    Stores a long but the datatype is xsd:integer
    StardogStringLiteral
    Representation of string literals without language tags.
    StardogValueFactory
    Implementation of a Sesame value factory for use by a Stardog store.
    StardogValueFactory.RDF  
    StardogValueFactory.RDFS  
    StatementPattern
    Sesame's Statement implementation that allows null SPOC elements which are interpreted as wildcards, thus representing a Statement pattern.
    StatementPattern.Builder  
    Values
    A convenience class to wrap a standard Sesame value factory to provide static value creation functions.
  • Enum Summary

    Enumeration of Stardog-supported XSD and RDF(S) datatypes.
